snippet.title: Chungo's Gauntlet Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Link: https://jane-chef.itch.io/chungos-gauntlet

Chungo's Gauntlet is an I Wanna be the Guy inspired adventure game with more than 70 levels. It uses a retro game aesthetic but also dabbles in some abstract styles.

Music Used:
Big Chungus - Endigo
Lion Heart - Gimmick!
Bothersome Guys - Mother 3
Megalovania (OST Version) - Super Smash Bros Ultimate (SiIvagunner Remix)
